### 1. Library Book Management API

# Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### Get book by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### Search books by title
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/search?title=Clean

### Add a new book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
    "author": "Andrew Hunt",
    "isbn": "978-0201616224",
    "publicationYear": 1999
}

### Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### 2. Student Registration API

# Get all students
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students

### Get student by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/1

### Get students by major
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/major/Computer%20Science

### Filter by GPA
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/filter?gpa=3.5

### Register a new student
POST http://localhost:8080/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Eva",
    "lastName": "Green",
    "email": "eva@example.com",
    "major": "Biology",
    "gpa": 3.7
}

### Update student info
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe Updated",
    "email": "john.updated@example.com",
    "major": "Computer Science",
    "gpa": 3.9
}

### 3. Restaurant Menu API

# Get all menu items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu

### Get menu item by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/1

### Get items by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/category/Appetizer

### Get available items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/available

### Search items by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menu/search?name=Chicken

### Add new menu item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pizza Margherita",
    "description": "Classic pizza with tomato and mozzarella",
    "price": 12.99,
    "category": "Main Course",
    "available": true
}

### Toggle availability
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/menu/1/availability

### Remove menu item
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/menu/1

### 4. E-Commerce Product API

# Get all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### Get all products with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products?page=1&limit=5

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### Get items by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/Electronics

### Get items by brand
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/brand/BrandA

### Search products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=phone

### Filter by price range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/price-range?min=100&max=500

### Get in-stock products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/in-stock

### Add new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Tablet",
    "description": "10-inch tablet",
    "price": 299.99,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "stockQuantity": 45,
    "brand": "BrandX"
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Smartphone Pro",
    "description": "Updated smartphone description",
    "price": 799.99,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "stockQuantity": 50,
    "brand": "BrandA"
}

### Update stock quantity
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/stock?quantity=100

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 5. Task Management API

# Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

### Get task by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

### Filter by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/status?completed=true

### Filter by priority
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/priority/HIGH

### Create task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Do Laundry",
    "description": "Wash and fold clothes",
    "completed": false,
    "priority": "LOW",
    "dueDate": "2023-11-20"
}

### Update task
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Assignment Complete",
    "description": "Submitted Spring Boot assignment",
    "completed": true,
    "priority": "HIGH",
    "dueDate": "2023-12-31"
}

### Mark as completed
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/2/complete

### Delete task
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/3

